00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:08,883
The important thing is everything from how they're dressed to their postures to their

206
00:12:08,883 --> 00:12:13,966
hair tells you something about these characters that you can immediately glean without even

207
00:12:13,966 --> 00:12:15,587
necessarily hearing them talk.

208
00:12:15,587 --> 00:12:17,207
So we use kind of those same strategies.

